Class Crop

java.lang.Object
Crop
Direct Known Subclasses:
FlowerCrop, RootCrop, TreeCrop
public abstract class Crop extends Object
Represents a crop that can be planted in the farm. Contains the crop's name, type, harvest time, water needs (and bonus), fertilizer needs (and bonus), minimum and maximum products produced, seed cost, selling price, and exp gain
